Figures 5, 6, and 7 depict how certain parameters can bring down the value of basic reproduction number below 1 and hence the epidemic potential. The contour plot (Fig. 5) shows that increase in the recovery rate of the asymptomatic individuals will result in reduction of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
